Attribute_Descr: The MAX returned among the previous Purchases of the Products where WHERE t2.online = 0
SQL_Query: SELECT t0.Purchase_ID, MAX(t2.returned) FROM Purchases t0  LEFT OUTER JOIN Products t1 ON t0.Product_ID = t1.Product_ID  LEFT OUTER JOIN Purchases t2 ON t1.Product_ID = t2.Product_ID AND t0.date > t2.date  WHERE t2.online = 0  GROUP BY t0.Purchase_ID

Attribute_Descr: The AVG returned among the previous Purchases of the Clients where AND t3.price > 1000.0 AND t3.price < 1000000.0
